{"tid":1497344,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[請向台灣文宣] 熱心男舉「台灣撐香港民主」紙牌 遭大媽暴打鬧「漢奸」","createTime":"2019-08-23T02:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T02:48:57.000Z","uid":46356,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"18a99d3b551a087067c3afb384e381061443d66a","tid":1497344,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T02:30:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190821/59955391\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190821%2F59955391&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1TUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=07e02188\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190821%2F59955391&h=5757cf58\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190821/59955391</a><br />\n熱心男舉「台灣撐香港民主」紙牌 遭大媽暴打鬧「漢奸」<br />\n<br />\n香港特首林鄭月娥無視百萬市民訴求，讓「反送中」抗爭持續超過2個月仍未平息，事件更撕裂普羅中國人，即使支持香港的人也遭針對，甚至遭遇暴力對待。近日就有網民拍到，一名男子在澳洲悉尼街頭高舉「台灣撐香港民主」的牌子，隨後被一名中國大媽在街頭對着他大喊「漢奸」，更一路追打。舉牌男子一個重心不穩跌倒後，大媽仍不停手，繼續用手袋暴打。<br />\n<br />\n內地網民當然未有譴責大媽，更「稱讚」大媽極具戰鬥力，還說：「你大媽還是你大媽」、「好樣的」、「支持大媽，愛我中華」。不過，亦有台灣人提出相反意見：「台灣人跟漢奸甚麼關係」、「譴責暴力」、「素質可見一斑」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，澳洲《坎培拉時報》報道，周六有多達3,000名親中人士走上街頭，大唱中國國歌之餘，還高叫「不愛香港的香港人滾出去」、「不愛中國，就是我們的敵人，把他們趕出去」等口號。當時一名披着青天白日旗的男子，與這群親中人士對陣，隨後雙方發生衝突。《坎培拉時報》記者更拍到披旗男子慘遭親中人士奪旗鎖喉，露出痛苦扭曲的表情。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果新聞網》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190821/large/1566350890_3d3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190821%2Flarge%2F1566350890_3d3c.jpg&h=2f3a8e51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n支持香港的男子在澳洲街頭被大媽暴打。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190821/large/1566351920_7704.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190821%2Flarge%2F1566351920_7704.jpg&h=f3057716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n披着青天白日旗的男子遭親中人士奪旗鎖喉。圖片:《坎培拉時報》"},{"pid":"bf0ef0e0e2b5cf6c9f959d2aecf31514bac941c2","tid":1497344,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T02:32:37.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">824 機場復活，WE WANT YOU！而家搭車犯法呀？</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9EGvnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9EGvnL.jpg&h=9da42bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WKSEg2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWKSEg2M.jpg&h=20a2e6bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/now5W2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnow5W2M.jpg&h=db034c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rC19Ef7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrC19Ef7.jpg&h=5ab15f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KUdLW2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKUdLW2O.jpg&h=132e85dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBGBjf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBGBjf8.jpg&h=8a441805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pgzvoHP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpgzvoHP.png&h=79a62f84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef4ab317e55378344b89c2a0fce63c5a70def163","tid":1497344,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T02:37:09.000Z","msg":"澳洲悉尼